videos.description: Omaha's Tre'Shawn Thurman rises up for the put back dunk.
videos.headline: Tre'Shawn Thurman hammers down the put back slam

videos.description: Tre'Shawn Thurman nails a 3-pointer on the break coming off a steal by Mitchell Hahn.
videos.headline: Omaha turns defense into offense to retake the lead

videos.description: Mike Daum up-fakes the defense, goes baseline and loses the ball, gets it back and slams down the dunk.
videos.headline: Mike Daum blows past the defense for a big dunk

videos.description: Chris Howell powers through contact for the layup plus the foul.

videos.description: Tre'Shawn Thurman comes up with a clutch block in the final minutes of play.

videos.description: Omaha's last second 3-pointer is no good allowing South Dakota State to clinch a birth to the NCAA tournament.
videos.headline: South Dakota State celebrates as they clinch a spot in the NCAA tournament
